","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"• Pruebas genéticas","guid":"uM2ZL-aHbhOGFqcX-0-MyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"34","text":"• ↳ Tto: IECA/ARA-II, BB, Antagonistas aldosterona,\\NAnticoagulación, CDI/RT, Trasplante","guid":"kViUeUPEGPjc71KxPVu8dA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"34","text":"• Variantes: MCD Periparto, Takotsubo, Familiar","guid":"OhlR32yj03s3T1QcCJhy3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"33","text":"2. MCP Restrictiva\\N(MCR)","guid":"r0iHPuueqOC-4IdxUloqBQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• ↳ Definición: ↓ Llenado diastólico (VI no dilatado, FEVI normal o casi normal)","guid":"rrxT8EF_Dzvbhom5T4dRSQ","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• ↳ Etiología:","guid":"9ZuV9xRIMWG-RMu-v5ZPlw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Infiltrativa: Amiloidosis, Sarcoidosis","guid":"LaRDQa-eDWXM75CX7kKXSQ","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Depósito: Enfermedad de Fabry, Hemocromatosis, Enfermedades de almacenamiento (Gaucher)","guid":"rKT3CzveVlunyZI06ZwxPA","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Fibrosis endomiocárdica","guid":"lqzPITr0c-81TJLDjdfRBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"• ↳ Clínica: IC derecha, Edema, Hepatomegalia, Ascitis, Arritmias","guid":"ejiRFWKM6bV4Cdy9XGIUxg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"• ↳ Dx:","guid":"00arB66MUFU44TbSChUlaw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Eco-Doppler: Patrón restrictivo (↑ Presión diastólica)","guid":"q1wnOtxTYijOhXvyaDgYhg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• RMN: Infiltración (amiloide), realce tardío","guid":"0NxBlwUUNFRe_tFUIgIkRg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Biopsia endomiocárdica: Confirma infiltrados","guid":"fC96sTU2munRI6kT4_wgXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"50","text":"• ↳ Tto: Manejo específico de la causa (amiloidosis, sarcoidosis), IC (diuréticos)","guid":"bOQSgI0Vx4yUe1eK3tdGLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"3